  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    Software Capability Improvement consists of&amp;nbsp;three practices:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
        href=&quot;./../../../practice.bus.sw_cap_prog_mgmt.base-ibm/guidances/practices/sw_cap_prog_mgmt_15255972.html&quot;&#xD;
        guid=&quot;_sh3v6CMmEd-VobohmWswkw&quot;>Software Capability Program Management&lt;/a> provides a standard approach for managing&#xD;
        software capability improvement that is aligned with the organization's strategic goals&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
        href=&quot;./../../../practice.bus.mdev.base/guidances/practices/method_development_99621E52.html&quot;&#xD;
        guid=&quot;_lFYasFImEd-S-5uzDh9e9Q&quot;>Method Development&lt;/a> describes how to&amp;nbsp;develop, implement,&amp;nbsp;and deploy&#xD;
        enterprise methods and tools&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLink&quot;&#xD;
        href=&quot;./../../../practice.bus.adopt_through_execution.base-ibm/guidances/practices/adopt_through_execution_7ACA1E5E.html&quot;&#xD;
         guid=&quot;_F5OpAG23Ed-vK5B6ZgVtPg&quot;>Adoption Through Execution&lt;/a> helps an organization develop a mentoring program in&#xD;
        order to drive successful adoption of capability improvements&lt;br />&#xD;
        &lt;br />&#xD;
        This overall Software Capability Improvement process is illustrated below:&lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    &lt;img height=&quot;415&quot; alt=&quot;Software Capability Improvement&quot; src=&quot;./resources/sw_cap_improve.gif&quot; width=&quot;600&quot; />&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    If the organization does not manage capability improvement as&amp;nbsp;a program,&amp;nbsp;process and tools adoption is at&#xD;
    risk. Without a managed program it is difficult to:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Provide objective evidence that the organization is improving&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Achieve successful adoption by managing risks&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    It is critical that the organizational software capability improvement team sees themselves as a service organization&#xD;
    measured by the success of the software development projects it supports.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
